Description: Display a website in a stripped down kiosk
 Display kiosk allows you to show a website fullscreen without any chrome
 around.
 .
 You can configure it to automatically scroll down at the desired speed.
 Whenever it reaches the bottom of the page it reloads and goes back up.
 .
 Uses include showing news on a public monitor.
